# WPA2 4-way handshake + post-association ENCRYPTED-DATA fuzzing.
# Needs -K (to derive the TK) and the NIC in active-monitor mode (hardware ACKs so
# the AP completes the handshake -> installs the TK). After M4, FUZZ_DATA repeatedly
# sends @send=encdata frames, which owfuzz CCMP-encrypts with the session TK; this
# fuzzes the encrypted-data parser AND keeps the STA alive (watchdog stays armed).
#
# in_state    | on_rx               | send       | goto_state
INIT          | START               | auth_open  | WAIT_AUTH
WAIT_AUTH     | AUTH                | assoc_req  | WAIT_ASSOC
WAIT_ASSOC    | ASSOCRES            | -          | WAIT_M1
WAIT_M1       | QOSDATA match=40:8a | m2         | WAIT_M3
WAIT_M3       | QOSDATA match=40:ca | m4         | FUZZ_DATA
FUZZ_DATA     | REPEAT              | encdata    | FUZZ_DATA
